item.title: CVE-2023-26316|2023-08-02T00:00:00 -- n%2Fa -- xiaomi%20cloud%20service%20application
item.description: A XSS vulnerability exists in the Xiaomi cloud service Application product. The vulnerability is caused by Webview's whitelist checking function allowing javascript protocol to be loaded and can be exploited by attackers to steal Xiaomi cloud service account's cookies.
